    "encrypted": "false",
    "display_name": "Network Security Engineer",
    "long_instructions": "## Network Security Engineer\r\n\r\nA **network security engineer** designs, implements, and maintains systems that protect an organization’s network from cyber threats and unauthorized access.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Chat with the network security engineer about your scenario. Figure out how the threat works and what harm it can cause.\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> It's the last day to submit college applications to a major university. Thousands of students begin uploading their forms, but suddenly the site slows to a crawl and eventually crashes. Based on this scenario, how does a DDoS attach work and why is it harmful?\r\n\r\n:::\r\n\r\n2. Chat with the network security engineer about **other ways to prevent DDoS attacks.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry using the following prompt:\r\n> What are ways to prevent DDoS attacks?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n3. Chat with the network security engineer about **the role of AI in preventing DDoS attacks.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How can AI detect and respond to a DDoS attack faster than human analysts?*\r\n> - *Can AI tell the difference between real users and fake traffic?*\r\n> - *How does AI help protect large-scale websites from being overwhelmed by malicious traffic?*\r\n:::\r\n\r\n4. Chat with the network security engineer about **ways that AI can make DDoS attacks more harmful.**\r\n\r\n:::details [Not sure where to start?]\r\nTry out the following prompts:\r\n> - *How might bad actors use AI in DDoS attacks, and what does that mean for defenders?*\r\n> - *How does AI change the threat landscape for DDoS attacks as a cyber threat?*\r\n:::",
